dao.interfaces

Interface CouponDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CouponDBDAO

    public interface CouponDAO
    The CouponDAO interface provides six basics methods for DML functionality and seven additional methods.
    The CouponDAO interface throws all exceptions to the throwable class CouponSystemException.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CouponDBDAO
    Version:
    1.00, 28/07/2016
    Author:
    Morris Elkanaev
